{EAST's 1\H opening is passed around to NORTH. He is 
tempted to overcall 1\S, but with 18 points is a little strong for a mere overcall. 
Instead, he doubles.

With 8 points SOUTH is not strong enough to jump. She bids 2\C.

NORTH now bids 2\S. By doubling first, then bidding his own suit, 
he shows a good suit and 17+ points.

SOUTH raises to 4\S.}

