{NORTH has 15 points and all the requirements for a Takeout Double of 1\S.

With 14 points of his own, SOUTH knows his side needs to be in a game somewhere. He passes this information 
to NORTH with a cue-bid of 2\S.

NORTH gets the message and starts the hunt for a trump fit by bidding 3\H. That 
makes it easy for SOUTH - he bids 4\H.}

